tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE quantum_error_rates (
	protocol_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	error_type VARCHAR(50),
	error_rate DECIMAL,
	timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE historical_data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    protocol_name VARCHAR(50),
    communication_type VARCHAR(50),
    data_received TEXT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE CommunicationLogs (
    log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    protocol_id INT,
    sender_id INT,
    receiver_id INT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
);
